{"tid":766060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不可能的湯神與子華神","createTime":"2018-08-03T09:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T09:45:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41bd67a42dc63ff2275e64153b38baaa80e7407b","tid":766060,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20180803/20467158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F20467158&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=914f3847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180803%2F20467158&h=53bd37a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20180803/20467158</a><br />\n<br />\n不可能的湯神與子華神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180803/large/1533202229_c271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180803%2Flarge%2F1533202229_c271.jpg&h=47ae520d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Mission Impossible　6》劇照<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nMI拍到第6集，是挑戰演藝界厭舊喜新的「不可能任務」。歷經22載，靚湯已由青靚小生變身神臂大叔嗎？放心，靚湯保養得宜，眼肚雖然難掩蓋，但56歲的人生滄桑味，只會增加亮點。神臂，倒是真的，電影宣傳做到滴水不漏，人盡皆知靚湯做多過講，真身落場，一雙神臂既能跳傘飛車又能引體爬上直升機，最後以神臂貼住懸崖峭壁，這個大叔搏到盡，電影內外，真假交替，一眼睇晒，靚湯，由頭到尾都落堅料，無添加，無防腐，啖啖心機。真心的，看湯哥特意拍短片對台灣觀眾交心就知，他稱台灣做Taiwan，正常不過，沒有為了大陸票房，雙膝跪叩。如果湯哥轉行，建議跳入熱廚房，做他的真靚湯廚神，這煲湯，22年夠陳，夠老火，夠窩心。<br />\n<br />\n「不可能」變可能，靚湯升呢變湯神。同樣在九七前發功的黃子華，也把棟篤笑推向不可能任務的至高境界。子華神宣告金盆  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n良　緣 (高慧然)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n郁風信中的梁愛詩 (林道群)"},{"pid":"17d3450b4cc8ff870bb2ca3a92246313bd68029d","tid":766060,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}